wallmemo - desktop note taking utility
===============================================================================

wallmemo is a small application to manage textual contents in a file, generate
a custom wallpaper and set it as background in Gnome3 desktop.

REQUIREMENTS
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
wallmemo depends on:

  - gio-2.0 >= 2.31.18
  - librsvg-2.0 >= 2.34.2

INSTALLATION
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
$ ./configure
$ make
# make install

